HEADWORD: Ghostly
<hw>Ghost"ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>gastlich</ets>,
<ets>gostlich</ets>, AS. <ets>g⟦amac⟧stlic</ets>. See
<er>Ghost</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Relating to the soul; not carnal
